    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">幻想</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>ENDURINGLY BELIEVE something that is NOT TRUE to be TRUE OR IMAGINE SOMETHING as REALthat is NOT REAL.</p>
    <div type="definition" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-13T01:37:18.877+09:00">
            <p>ENDURINGLY IMAGINED to be REAL WHEN IT is NOT REAL.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>This concept was elaborated in Buddhism, but transferred uses of words like xū 虛 "empty, illusory" do perhaps convey the meaning in pre-Buddhist Chinese.</p>
        </div>
